⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The Dogs
node AFM · AFM · ⟦The Dogs:AFM:6097b6⟧

WHO   — The Dogs — the secret police
WHAT  — The instrument of terror beneath the propaganda: they drive out Snowball and execute the ‘confessors’ in the purges.
WHERE — AFM · ANIMAL FARM  Framework inputs: Animal Farm (George Orwell, 1945)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because behind every rewritten commandment is a fang — propaganda persuades, but the dogs enforce.
HOW   — By being raised apart, loyal only to Napoleon, and loosed to kill or expel on command.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I am the fang under the slogan — Squealer talks you into it, but I am the reason no one finishes the sentence that begins ‘but—’.

